so need a car for When will the new Maxima come out by the way model year I I would very much appreciate your input in Please reply by e mail preferred or post in this Craig Thanks Ryan Ryan Kim University of Toronto EECG Computer Graphics Do not weave between traffic cones at road from the new British Highway Code Toronto Star April